        "description": "It would be nice if a \"LargeMap\" type existed along side the \"Map\" type for parity. For other datatypes that require offset arrays/buffers, such as String, List, BinaryArray, provides a \"large\" version of these types, i.e. LargeString, LargeList, and LargeBinaryArray. It would be nice to have a \"LargeMap\" for parity.",
